These are Puzzles for 6x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, mirinda
There 2 different types of food: peas, cabbage
City: san-francisco, marseilles
There are 2 different nationalities: french, malaysian
2 different pets are kept: ferret, goat
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: poppy, aconite
1. the owner of the goat is on the far left##1
2. the person eating peas is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1
3. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1
4. the french is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |
| Beverage      | milk       | mirinda    |
| Food           | cabbage | peas |
| City   | marseilles     | san-francisco   |
| Nationality   | malaysian  | french     |
| Pet           | goat       | ferret     |
| Flower     | poppy     | aconite        |

