.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, water
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: ice-hockey, parkour
There are 2 different favourite colors: emerald, white
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, pop
2 different pets are kept: bird, rat
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: june, october
1. the fan of pop is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
2. the person drinking water is the fan of pop##1
3. the person who likes emerald is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
4. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |
| Beverage      | 7up        | water   |
| Sport         | parkour | ice-hockey |
| Color   | emerald     | white   |
| Music-Genre   | folk       | pop     |
| Pet           | rat        | bird    |
| Birthday     | june  | october    |

